 a theft while hunting for monsters.\n\n## More on this story\n\n  * The power of Pokemon nostalgia\n\n    * Published\n\n16 July 2016\n\n  * How Pokemon Go locations work (probably)\n\n    * Published\n\n15 July 2016\n\n  * Pokemon Go unleashed in the UK\n\n    * Published\n\n14 July 2016\n\n## Top Stories\n\n  * 'Don't' - Biden warns Iran against attacking Israel\n\n    * Published\n\n2 hours ago\n\n  * 'Huge amount' of Gaza surgery on children - UK doctor\n\n    * Published\n\n8 hours ago\n\n  * Kamala Harris blames Trump for Arizona abortion law\n\n    * Published\n\n32 minutes ago\n\n## Features\n\n  * How a North Korean missile researcher became a South Korean MP\n\n  * Engineers in Oregon train dog robot to walk on Moon. VideoEngineers in Oregon train dog robot to walk on Moon\n\n  * The migrant story shining a light on Gulf states' exploitation\n\n  * Suicide is on the rise for young Americans. Why?\n\n  * 'I survived the ferry disaster - but lost 17 of my family'\n\n  * Weekly quiz: How did 'Hardest Geezer' celebrate the end of his Africa run?\n\n  * A simple guide to India's general election\n\n  * OJ Simpson: His life and the trial that defined it. VideoOJ Simpson: His life and the trial that defined it\n\n  * South Korean leader learns political cost of a spring onion\n\n## Elsewhere on the BBC\n\n  * On the trip of a lifetime, which pair will finish first?\n\nFive teams of intrepid Brits battle it out in a breath-taking 15,000 kilometre\nrace\n\n  * Reporting on the OJ Simpson car chase\n\nFormer LA crime reporter, David Goldstein, recalls the most \u2018surreal\u2019 day of\nhis career\n\n  * Ancient artefacts, power play and exploring epic locations\n\nMary Beard uncovers the hidden world of the Roman emperors\n\n  * From Doctor Who to An Enemy of the People\n\nNihal Arthanayake brings you an in-depth interview with actor Matt Smith\n\n## Most Read\n\n  1. 1\n\n'Don't' - Biden warns Iran against attacking Israel\n\n  2. 2\n\nVietnamese billionaire sen